text: Jussi Nordqvist (27 May 1917 - 15 August 1989) was a Finnish sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, prone event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Finnish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Finland Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
